	<h1 class="title">阿兰·德波顿这座假日小屋，“让客人沉浸在极度平静之中”</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/161922/small/161922.jpg?1442322894" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">廖婷 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2016-04-26 07:51:16 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/25976/medium/25976.jpeg?1461574076" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


